{"word":"προεξανίσταμαι","slug":"προεξανίσταμαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προεξανίσταμαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, with aor2, <a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a>, and plup. <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>to rise and go out before</i> or <i>first</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>in a race, <i>to start before</i> the signal is given, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}